9,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7cbc75fe9ef7fd4e6df4d74ccf87ea4631d68150","tid":2083983,"uid":61547,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T06:07:22.000Z","msg":"[稍日向] 明日、世界が終わるなら"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T06:40:34.000Z","msg":"大師<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"499d34837e23f1912e5824cba839d81e7afa9ba1","tid":2083983,"uid":46155,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"7d1de4b7250e87ce09ba6868dcccd089ead039af","tid":2083983,"uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7cd7475c2a25c740bf188f36c11ef455c3d96b08","tid":2083983,"uid":46155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T06:37:54.000Z","msg":"扑野就扑野啦, 係要寫到懶係煽情為咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T06:39:36.000Z","msg":"幾有意思wor套野<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n扑野根本就唔重要 呢套野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T06:45:20.000Z","msg":"咁我睇H漫黎做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"944a781b2f9fe1316a415772b1c525c90e8231b1","tid":2083983,"uid":91931,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T06:55:20.000Z","msg":"D評論仲好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有趣的題材<br />\n雖然將男主降智商強制Bad End 但其實若有好好營造的話這並不損悲愴感<br />\n首先沒有描寫男主和魔王的羈絆逐漸加深的過程<br />\n跳過這過程使得魔王前段傲得很公式 後段嬌得太突然<br />\n草草打一炮後進入收尾 徒留隔靴搔癢之憾<br />\n男主應該是在一成不變的工程師生涯中偶然尋得真愛 日復一日的倦怠中好似漸漸地有了一點光芒<br />\n而魔王從一心擊敗勇者 到最後要說出&quot;明天見啦!&quot; 好像勇者的事也不太重要了<br />\n以魔王的身分懷抱這樣純純的少女之戀 隨著劇情可以自然又巧妙的揭露<br />\n這充滿潛力與反差萌的設定居然沒有好好利用 真是太可惜了<br />\n第二是沒有完全發揮劇情的催淚之處<br />\n高傲的魔王日日盼望著迎戰勇者<br />\n可是勇者卻從不曾到來 僅管如此魔王依然全力備戰<br />\n對男主展示得意的招式 卻渾然不知已不再被需要 只是過氣糞Game裡待銷毀的資料<br />\n這悲傷的設定應該多花點篇幅刻畫的<br />\n而男主明白一切卻又愛上可愛的魔王因此不捨結束這哀傷的故事<br />\n最後男主應該是要懷著這樣複雜的心情 百般無奈甚至被迫地畫下句點才對<br />\n結果竟然爽快地點下YES 整個感覺就變成爽完閃人的無恥人渣<br />\n第24頁的表情從依依不捨的道別 變得比較像是是打定主意白嫖的嫖客開溜前那一閃即逝的廉價罪惡感<br />\n前面的眼淚都變得好虛偽<br />\n<br />\n結論：分成兩集會更好 讚美貓頭鷹"},{"pid":"fc8e1ad6fd02a725991602024c726705024e634c","tid":2083983,"uid":198175,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T07:01:54.000Z","msg":"如果個主角係隻game嘅IT佬, 其實可以偷雞backup咗個NPC data同server core, 返屋企起返個private server, 7x24又好, 得閒先開嚟login又好, 只有幾個NPC要run, 你搞台2/3手 server都頂到啦"},{"pid":"a0e3d726a738ca308b05ebf8fdbeab7ca9d6efd3","tid":2083983,"uid":33783,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7cbc75fe9ef7fd4e6df4d74ccf87ea4631d68150","tid":2083983,"uid":61547,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T06:07:22.000Z","msg":"[稍日向] 明日、世界が終わるなら"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T09:51:28.000Z","msg":"快到一個點<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c972b971ae2d8a28c6ba17db4c774f7bda71adf","tid":2083983,"uid":13808,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7cbc75fe9ef7fd4e6df4d74ccf87ea4631d68150","tid":2083983,"uid":61547,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T06:07:22.000Z","msg":"[稍日向] 明日、世界が終わるなら"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T10:05:35.000Z","msg":"一刀羅剎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"718cb90ceb92fe3f0d94df58ffb950ccef60d622","tid":2083983,"uid":52939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T10:07:39.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"0df790875a14972d77946af5b3acd5041472111e","tid":2083983,"uid":261873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T13:00:15.000Z","msg":"中出即刪ser<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d3a3526cdc5da4fd1a26660437379872ef84bc3","tid":2083983,"uid":46155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fc8e1ad6fd02a725991602024c726705024e634c","tid":2083983,"uid":198175,"like":2,"disli